body.description: At MAM we work with medical experts to anticipate your baby's needs from day one. Whether you're using baby formula or expressed breast milk, MAM bottles will support you every step of the way. MAM Easy Active Bottles have a SkinSoft textured nipple that is easily accepted by babies. The anti-slip surface at the base helps to keep it in baby's mouth, so MAM nipples are often accepted by babies when other nipples are not.The flat shape of the nipple fits perfectly in your baby's mouth, making the switch between breast and bottle easy. The ergonomically-designed bottle is easy for both parents and babies to hold, and the wide neck makes filling and cleaning easy. The bottles are also compatible with Slow Flow (0+ months), Medium Flow (2+ months), Fast Flow (4+ months), and Extra Fast Flow (6+ months) nipples.This set includes two MAM Fast Flow Silicone Nipples, accepted by 94% of babies. The bottle is made from BPS and BPA free materials. *Medical study 2011 / Market research 2010, tested with 204 mothers. ** Market research 2009-2020, tested with 1,572 babies .

For over 45 years we've been obsessed with making innovative pacifiers, bottles, cups, teethers, and toothbrushes, providing babies with optimal care at all stages. The nipple's flat shape fits perfectly in baby's mouth, making the switch back-and-forth between breast and bottle easy. The ergonomic shape makes it easy to hold for parents and babies and the wide neck makes filling and cleaning easy. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We love, love, love, all the MAM products! My son struggled eating from other bottle brands, and a friend suggest these! They were a game changer for us, and we will never use another brand! MAM bottles are easy to clean, easy for the baby to use, and are long lasting! We have had no issues with cracks or mold. The bottle doesn’t have complicated parts to clean. You twist off the bottle from the bottom container. All bottle brushes fit into this too!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute, durable and easy to clean
reviews.reviewText: We love these bottles. We've been using MAM bottles for the last 2 years with our toddler and our baby girl. They are easy to clean and are made of great material. They go in the bottle sterilizer with no issues. Our children have had no trouble transitioning to different flow size nipples with this brand. Definitely recomment

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 5, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I love this brand, when I got these bottles it looked like I got them from Target. Everything looked pretty good and nothing was missing, occasionally there is some leaking but I'm not sure if that's because I need new nipples again, if its an issue with the bottle, or if it's just user error and I didn't pull the nipple all the way through. It happens are the most random rushed times and when it does leak on the occasion its leaking when I shake it between the nipple and they grey cap.

reviews.reviewText: Casi no doy opiniones de los productos, pero esta vez si daré mi comentario tengo un baby de 4 meses y solo le daba mi pecho.
